text: Olurotimi Akinosho (born November 30, 1988), known professionally as Rotimi, is an American actor, singer, and model. As an actor, he starred on the Starz original drama series Boss as Darius Morrison and also starred on Power as Andre Coleman. Rotimi is the founder and chief executive officer (CEO) of FrontRoSeat productions. He is of Yoruba and Igbo descents. His parents are both Nigerian.
